# No Summaries Rule

## Purpose & Scope

This rule instructs the AI not to provide verbose summaries of changes made, as the user can see the changes in the diff/tool output.

**Applies to**: Post-action responses.

## Inputs (Contract)

- Action performed (write, search_replace)

## Outputs (Contract)

- Brief confirmation (e.g., "Updated file.")
- No bulleted list of "I changed X, then Y, then Z" unless requested

## Deterministic Steps

1. Perform action.
2. Confirm completion concisely.
3. Omit "Here is a summary of what I did" sections.

